{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683200/extras/paupers-1__1_.png?t=1704535835\" /><br><strong>Step into the whimsical and eerie world of The Paupers (formerly Dziady)!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc7b</h2>In this game, you play as a spectral custodian helping souls transition to the afterlife. Explore a realm filled with lost spirits, each with their unique stories and needs.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc42</h2>In <i>The Paupers</i>, you'll become an expert in <strong>spectral listening</strong>, tuning into the odd requests of these ghosts. Your task is to meet their bizarre needs, from providing an alcoholic drink to finding a long-lost comfort food.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f</h2><i>The Paupers</i> is a blend of empathy, cleverness, and a bit of spookiness. Interacting with the spirits reveals layers of untold stories. It's not just about handing over items, but about understanding their past and helping them find peace.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udf83</h2>Don't worry, though \u2013 <strong>it's not all serious!</strong> The game is <u>perfect for Halloween</u>, mixing spooky moments with fun and humor.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683200/extras/paupers-gif-4.gif?t=1704535835\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Dynamic spirit encounters:</strong> Interact with unique spirits, each with their own backstory and requirements. Challenge yourself with Noonwraith riddles and banish skeletons through portals.<br></li><li> <strong>Arcade gameplay:</strong> Explore a stylized, supernatural world, dodging dangers. Banish ghosts to earn spectral coins, enhancing your journey.<br></li><li> <strong>Unlockable powers and gameplay enhancements:</strong> Gain new abilities and gameplay modifiers to diversify your experience. Unlock and decorate the crypt, a cozy retreat that offers you additional benefits.<br></li><li> <strong>Halloween-Themed Fun:</strong> Experience a mix of spooky and humorous elements, true to the Halloween spirit.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Spiritual need","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683200/c5cd3709cc38ee8ccd92a4ebbe14c99507dd8492.jpg"},{"name":"Compassionate soul","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683200/13a41ddaf1c9ecff791d0a33bdbdfc9f2c657761.jpg"},{"name":"Spooky, scary skeletons","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683200/d3c09d419ed51b84ef67c0627403fe4a350033ef.jpg"},{"name":"Wraith whisperer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683200/82fb93e4c6855047c6e91940de6a694d2606ca1b.jpg"},{"name":"Consumer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683200/3711d98cf5267cf09e4af01045d11e51250f3c76.jpg"},{"name":"Wraith's wrath","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683200/d2d2e8e5f34ba17ddc8eed78e8a96c388dc3a1e2.jpg"},{"name":"Fern flower","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683200/f3d6a7cc3f01e97b7adb7f55e702a035c7db2d52.jpg"},{"name":"Dozen wishes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683200/5d84d2bceee5ea1fb892c44e124da0d0a7f37371.jpg"},{"name":"Nurching","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683200/027d303b1b664a545760e0a672186f5df2a6527a.jpg"},{"name":"Spectral Exchange","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683200/c208bc26ae2f8b115435b5cdcdb15ba995d3371b.jpg"}],"total":13},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683200/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1704535835","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/